Elastic net linear regression using ‘glmnet’

80-20 training-test split. Training sample N=4638, test sample N=1120. Although glmnet standardises data by default, coefficients are returned on their original scales. To get standardised coefficients for applying to other data, I’m scaling the raw data before inputting to glmnet. 31 predictors were included, including an interaction between bullying and gender.
